        text: "\n\u201c\u015eiir; var\u0131lmaz\u0131n \u00f6tesinde, d\u00f6rt kenarl\u0131, a\u00e7\u0131s\u0131z bir \u00fc\u00e7gendir.\u201d (A. Ka\u00e7ar)\n\u015eiir, k\u00fclt\u00fcrlerin edeb\u00ee miras\u0131n\u0131n en temel \u00f6gelerinden biridir. Zira her \u015fiir asl\u0131nda ait oldu\u011fu topraklar\u0131n \u00e7ok y\u00f6nl\u00fc bir yans\u0131mas\u0131d\u0131r. Konu se\u00e7iminden dil \u00f6zelliklerine ve \u00fcslup niteliklerine kadar \u015fiiri tamamlayan t\u00fcm unsurlar, \u015fairin hem i\u00e7 d\u00fcnyas\u0131n\u0131n hem de ya\u015fad\u0131\u011f\u0131 toplumun sosyal kabullerinin bir nevi aynas\u0131d\u0131r. Bu kitab\u0131n konusu olan Ahmet Ka\u00e7ar da as\u0131rlar\u0131n gelene\u011fini ruhuna sindirerek derin g\u00f6zlem g\u00fcc\u00fc, hassas duyu\u015f kabiliyeti, engin birikimi ve nevi \u015fahs\u0131na m\u00fcnhas\u0131r \u00fcslubuyla m\u0131sralar boyunca insan\u0131 ve toplumu anlatm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\u00d6te yandan kabul g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f bir kan\u0131d\u0131r ki her \u015fiirin hakikati \u015fairinin g\u00f6nl\u00fcnde gizlidir. Lakin her ne kadar bir \u015fiirin \u00fczerine s\u00f6ylenecek her s\u00f6z eksik kalsa; imgelerin, metaforlar\u0131n ard\u0131na gizlenen ifadelerdeki maksat daima \u015fairin ruhunda mahfuz olsa da dizelerden y\u00fckselen sesleri duymak, insan\u0131 ve hayat\u0131 yeni bir solukla i\u00e7ine \u00e7ekmenin e\u015fsiz bir yoludur. H\u00e2liyle Ka\u00e7ar\u2019\u0131n \u015fiirlerine kulak veren bu \u00e7al\u0131\u015fma da kendimizi ve ya\u015fam\u0131 farkl\u0131 perdelerden okumam\u0131za vesile olacak; bu d\u00fcnya y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc bir de onun zihninin ve y\u00fcre\u011finin g\u00f6z\u00fcyle g\u00f6rmemizin kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 aralayacakt\u0131r.\n\u00a0\n(Tan\u0131t\u0131m B\u00fclteninden)\n\u00a0\n",
